# ── Local dev ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# No setup needed. Game state saves to game-data.json automatically.

# ── Vercel deployment — Supabase ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Create a free project at https://supabase.com
# 2. Project Settings → API → copy Project URL and anon key below
# 3. For SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN: https://supabase.com/dashboard/account/tokens
#    → Generate new token (needed once to auto-create the database table)
# 4. Add all three to Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables
# 5. Deploy, then visit https://your-app.vercel.app/api/setup  ← creates the table automatically
# 6. Visit /api/debug to confirm everything works

SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here
SUPABASE_ACCESS_TOKEN=your-personal-access-token-here
